## Project: SLAB Builders HUB

### Stack
- React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind CSS, shadcn-ui, React Router v6
- Data: Supabase (all data is cloud-synced, no mock data, no localStorage for app data)
- Deploy: Vercel

### DO NOT MODIFY these files (they are working and connected to production):
- src/integrations/supabase/client.ts
- src/integrations/supabase/types.ts
- src/coi-tracker/integrations/supabase/client.ts
- src/coi-tracker/integrations/supabase/types.ts
- src/contexts/ProjectContext.tsx
- .env
- vite.config.ts
- tailwind.config.ts
- package.json (do not add/remove dependencies without asking)

### DO NOT:
- Replace Supabase calls with mock data or localStorage
- Change Supabase URLs or keys
- Modify authentication or data-fetching logic unless explicitly asked
- Create new config files or overwrite existing ones
- Remove or rename existing imports/exports that other files depend on

### WHEN EDITING UI:
- Use existing shadcn-ui components from @/components/ui/
- Use Tailwind classes for styling
- Keep the existing color scheme (accent: #c37e87, text: #7b7c81)
- Preserve all existing Supabase data-fetching and mutation logic in page components
- Only change visual/layout code, not data logic, unless asked
